{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"4647483edb","title":"给章士钊的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"a76a837bb8","index":0,"year":1966,"month":1,"day":12,"articleId":"4647483edb"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"57eea82497","name":"康生","type":"人物"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji48","name":"毛泽东全集第48卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/48-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji48":{"comments":[{"id":"e5f117f056","publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"4647483edb","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"章士钊，字行严，当时任全国人大常委会委员、中央文史研究馆馆长。"},{"id":"987cb9c4c2","publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"4647483edb","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"《三国志》，西晋陈寿摆写的一部纪传体魏、蜀、吴三国史，分魏志、蜀志、吴志，共六十万卷。三志原本各自独立，后世将它合为一书。"},{"id":"80f1c883c8","publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"4647483edb","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"《柳文指要》，是章士钊所著的一部专门研究唐代文学家柳宗元文集的著作。1965年8月5日，毛泽东曾将这部书稿批转给中共中央书记处书记康生阅读。12月5日，康生给毛泽东写信说，“我读完之后，觉得主席八月五日信中对此书的评价，是十分中肯完全正确的。“因此书有些人已知道主席看过，所以我提了几点意见，用纸条标出。请主席着看，是否需要作词句的删改。《柳文指要》一书，后经作者修改，在1971年由中华书局正式出版。"},{"id":"c723cdb832","publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"4647483edb","index":4,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指康生1965年12月5日给毛泽东的信。"}],"contents":[{"id":"f2d093c327","type":"title","text":"给章士知的信","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"4647483edb"},{"id":"e5f117f056","type":"paragraph","text":"行严先生：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"4647483edb"},{"id":"987cb9c4c2","type":"paragraph","text":"一九六五年十二月十六日惠书及附件均已收读，极为感谢！三国志P一部亦已收到，可作纪念，便时艺代致谢意。大著《柳文指要》康生同志已读完交来问，兹送上。有若干字句方面的意见，是否有当，请的定。顺颂","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"4647483edb"},{"id":"80f1c883c8","type":"subtitle","text":"春安","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"4647483edb"},{"id":"c723cdb832","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"4647483edb"},{"id":"1d228ef3ea","type":"paragraph","text":"一九六六年一月十二日附件两纸，另康生同志来信一件，均附上。又及","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"4647483edb"}],"page":{"id":"e741f80b34","publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"4647483edb","start":292,"end":293}}}},"__N_SSG":true}